<section xml:id="unit-testing_introduction-unit-testing">
  <title>Introduction: Unit Testing</title>
  <p>Testing plays an important role in the development of software. To this point, most of the testing you have done has probably involved
            running your program and fixing errors as you notice them. In this chapter, you will learn about a more methodical approach to testing.
            Along the way, you will pick up some design techniques. So, let's get started!</p>
</section>
